  Text: |-
    Connected Lenses - Laser Pointer 
    
    This example demonstrate a popular pattern for multiplayer game, "Laser Pointer". In this shared experience players will be able to aim to an object and pinch to leave a "mark" on the object.   Build the lens on two devices. 
    Aim to the vase object, leave your mark. 
    All of the players will be able to see it. 
    
    The mark will be visible for all of the other players.  
